  "projectName": "PX4 NuttX",
  "projectDescription": "Apache NuttX is a standards-compliant, highly configurable real-time operating system (RTOS) with PX4 patches for drone autopilot hardware including Pixhawk, STM32F4/F7/H7, i.MX RT, and Kinetis platforms.",
